                <!-- Our Process (Optional, but good for SEO and user trust) -->
                <section class="service-feature-wifi" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <h2>Our Wi-Fi Solution Process</h2>
                    <p>UDCOMMS follows a meticulous process to deliver optimal Wi-Fi performance:</p>
                    <ol>
                        <li><strong>Site Survey & Assessment:</strong> We conduct a thorough analysis of your premises to identify coverage gaps, interference sources, and unique requirements.</li>
                        <li><strong>Custom Design:</strong> Based on the assessment, we design a bespoke Wi-Fi network layout, selecting appropriate hardware (APs, controllers) and configurations.</li>
                        <li><strong>Professional Installation:</strong> Our certified technicians ensure precise installation and optimal placement of all equipment, minimizing disruption to your operations.</li>
                        <li><strong>Testing & Optimization:</strong> We perform comprehensive testing (signal strength, speed, coverage) and fine-tune settings for peak performance.</li>
                        <li><strong>Ongoing Support & Maintenance:</strong> We offer continued support, monitoring, and maintenance to ensure your Wi-Fi network remains reliable and secure.</li>
                    </ol>
